Class GraphNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • influencer.GraphNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<GraphNode>

    public class GraphNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<GraphNode>
    Representation of a single user in the social network graph. Vertices are represented as an integer. Edges are stored in HashMap with node number of the other node keyed to the weight of the edge (how many times this node and the other retweeted.
